HEADWORD: Steadfastly
<hw>Stead"fast*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a steadfast manner;
firmly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Steadfastly</qex> believe that whatever God has revealed is
infallibly true.</q> <rj><qau>Wake.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Steadfastness</ent>⟦br⟧
